Install java 8 open JDK
Install java 11 open JDK
Install eclipse IDE
Install openssh-server
Install Notepad++
(Install glassfish)
Install curl
(Install Node.js, express.js, socket-io, socket-io.client)
(Install netty-socketIO and netty-socketIO-demo)

Download Hadoop 2.7.7 and follow instructions on https://hadoop.apache.org/docs/r2.7.7/hadoop-project-dist/hadoop-common/SingleCluster.html 
add hadoop.tmp.dir and mapreduce.output.fileoutputformat.outputdir to core-site.xml (Use any path which is permanent)!

In .bashrc (for yarn session, but did not work):
	export HADOOP_HOME=/home/aljoscha/hadoop-2.7.7
	export HADOOP_CLASSPATH=`/home/aljoscha/hadoop-2.7.7/bin/hadoop classpath`

Download HBase 1.4.3 and follow instructions on https://hbase.apache.org/book.html#quickstart to "Pseudo-Distributed for Local Testing"

Install git
git clone graph-vis project
git clone apache/flink project
git clone graph-viewport-driven project




